column5: Will be taking any and all offers for this. Not sure of the regs getting across the border.  fishsuit.pdf
BWAhahahahahaha ,Who would wear such a thing  I,ll bet the best bait for that one would be an Oscar myer and musturd. HAHA  To funny.

Thanks for posting this. It was a comical photo.  I had my face painted to look like a fish one Halloween, when I used to do an outdoors column in Eastern Ontario, in Kingston. The job was amazing, with the only photo taken could never be found. I had scales and texture, and would describe it as a "McFish", given that one could not tell if it was a coldwater or warmwater species.  outdoorguy61
Definately raised the "gaydar" on this one.
The guy in the fish costume really doesn't look too happy, does he?
Thanks, I almost sprayed my monitor with the water I was drinking! LOL

I don't know what your preferences are there sirfish but I'll only spawn with hens. I'm happy in the pic because we took 2nd place behind the fighting coke driver/pepsi drivers it's just that the picture takers were laughing so hard I was confused.
